  <generalInformation><![CDATA[<p>It's up to you to decide between the warm, wooden resort of <a data-udi="umb://document/799f63184c52477c94171a057c16e540" href="/{localLink:umb://document/799f63184c52477c94171a057c16e540}" title="Avoriaz">Avoriaz</a> or the traditional mountain village of <a data-udi="umb://document/957b02edc6d846dfb4b2a1b2d1a3222d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/957b02edc6d846dfb4b2a1b2d1a3222d}" title="Morzine">Morzine</a>, but with both resorts come the limitless adventures of the Portes du Soleil ski area where you can start your journey in France and finish in Switzerland - travel across the border with your skis still on your feet!</p>]]></generalInformation>
